description: Nicknamed the "cattle car," the LB-77a is designed to ferry EVA suited workers to job sites in local space as cheaply as possible. In the OKLG Boneyard it's not unusual to see dozens of spacers packed onto the vessel, clinging to cargo webbing, half of them mooing as a joke.
